Classes
Class
Description
AnalysisSoftwareElement
Base element for a term that is defined in a controlled vocabulary, with OPTIONAL value.
BaseQuality
Element containing metadata and qualityMetrics for a single run.
ControlledVocabulary
Element describing a controlled vocabulary used to refer to the source of the used CV terms in qualityMetric objects (and others).
Converter
Provides convenience functions to parse date and time strings and to serialize and deserialize mzQC from and to a variety of sources.
Coordinate
JSON schema specifying the mzQC format v1.0.0 developed by the HUPO-PSI Quality Control working group (http://psidev.info/groups/quality-control).

Base element for a term that is defined in a controlled vocabulary, with OPTIONAL value.
InputFile

Metadata describing the QC analysis.
MzQC
Root element of an mzQC file.
QualityMetric
Element containing the value and description of a QC metric defined in a controlled vocabulary.
Unit
One or more controlled vocabulary elements describing the unit of the metric.
